      <body>Would another way around this be to hook method_added and use that? 
The reason I say that is that typically when I have had this problem it hasn't really been at the point of migration. If I had a column and stuff breaks then I know where to go.

Much harder to diagnose is when a column you already have starts shadowing an important method, for example in one app I had a changed attribute that became problematic when I moved apps to 2.1 (clashes with dirty)</body>
